title: The.Batman.S05E01.The.Batman-Superman.Story.Pt.1[cabra].mkv
description:
Why do the writers keep ruining everything that&#039;s good? Superman/Batman stories are such a rich source of great material and yet here we get crap. I mean WTH! Superman is the angsty recluse and Batman is saying go team go? At least Batgirl wasn&#039;t in this episode, talk about character assassination.

Props to the animator who made Lex&#039;s building, that was the highlight for me.
